  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fast Track Education for Afghan Women and Girls</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educating females is the best way to accelerate equality in society for women and girls.   Many female refugees lose out on education when they are displaced, either to a foreign country or internally in Afghanistan. We provide fast track classes in literacy, mobile literacy (learning through texting), tailoring, computing, English and other subjects to thousands of women and girls. Many of our students are former refugees, returned from Iran or Pakistan or internally displaced persons.</narrative>
  </description>
